data.description: This stunning townhome in Lakewood Ranch is conveniently located near downtown Lakewood Ranch, downtown Waterside, UTC Mall, Polo grounds, and the pristine waters of the Gulf of Mexico. A beautiful kitchen with solid service counter tops is the center of attention!  This unit boasts a bright and functional design featuring a laundry room on the bedroom level for added convenience. There's a two car garage, driveway, and visitors spots close by for visiting guests. Enjoy the elegance of light tiled floors throughout  along with beautifully tiled baths and upgraded vanities.  The patio and two balconies offer a picturesque preserve view. Come check out this contemporary home today and start enjoying a maintenance free lifestyle! Roof and AC 2023 !
